🚀 TMUX CHEAT SHEET (Custom Config)
  -----------------------------------------
  PREFIX: Control + Space (C-Space)

  🪟 WINDOWS (Tabs at bottom)
  New Window:     Prefix + c
  Rename Window:  Prefix + ,
  Next / Prev:    Prefix + n / p
  Switch by #:    Prefix + 0-9
  Last Window:    Prefix + Tab

  🪓 PANES (Splits)
  Vertical:       Prefix + |
  Horizontal:     Prefix + -
  Switch:         Prefix + Arrows
  Resize:         Prefix + Arrows (Hold/Tap)
  Zoom (Full):    Prefix + z
  Close Pane:     Prefix + x

  🛠️ ADVANCED & NAVIGATION
  Join Pane:      Prefix + j
  Send Pane:      Prefix + s
  Scroll/Copy:    Prefix + [  (q to exit)
  Reload Config:  Prefix + r
  -----------------------------------------
